==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dziggetai
<hw>Dzig"ge*tai</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>The kiang, a wild horse or wild ass of Tibet (<spn>Asinus
hemionus</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The name is sometimes applied also to the koulan or
onager. See <er>Koulan</er>.</note></p>

